{"word":"G4220 - πότερον - póteron - pot'-er-on - Whether","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">πότερον</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">póteron</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">pot'-er-on</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Whether</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Conjunction / இணைப்புச்சொல்</span>"},{"paragraph":"இரண்டில் - ஒன்று"},{"paragraph":"which of two"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>Neuter of a comparative of the base of <a href=\"#/G4226 - ποῦ - poû - poo/4226\">G4226</a>; interrogitive as adverb, <i>which</i> (of two), that is, <i>is it</i> this or that: - whether.</span>"},{"paragraph":""}]}